		<h2>Group currency generated and distributed among social networks</h2>
		<div class="newsletter">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 tagline">
					<img class="accent-left" src="/assets/landing_accent_left.png"/>Beam and Earn Reps<br>at Mysteryland and Other Events<img class="accent-right" src="/assets/landing_accent_right.png" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="newsletter-form container">
				<div class="row">
